item.title: beginning my hackthebox challenge.
item.description: This is the first post on my new blog, I have 2 main objectives for this blog. -Create content so I can learn revise and refine my learning. -Provide a resource for myself to look back at and be proud of writing. I will aim to post 2x writeups aswell as learning notes throughout each Introduction to Go Templates Go templates provide an extremely simple template language. It adheres to the belief that only the most basic of logic belongs in the template or view layer.
